                以全球化的视野，我们产品覆盖全球多个国家，提供多语言、多地域的服务，让用户无障碍畅享产品。
              </p>
              <a
                class="link link-primary link-hover mt-2 inline-flex items-center"
                href=""
                ><span></span>
                <svg
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  class="w-4 h-4 ml-2"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="step" class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col text-center w-full mb-20">
          <h1 class="sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-medium mb-4">轻松上手</h1>
          <p
            class="lg:w-2/3 mx-auto text-base text-base-content/90 whitespace-break-spaces"
          >
            不论你是新手还是经验丰富的用户，我们的引导将带你穿越每个关键步骤，让你在短时间内轻松上手。开始你的探索之旅，尽情享受应用带来的便捷和乐趣！
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap w-full" x-data="{ tab: 1 }">
          <div
            class="lg:w-2/5 md:w-1/2 md:pr-10 h-full max-h-screen overflow-y-auto"
          >
            <ul class="steps steps-vertical">
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 1 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 1"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">注册与登录</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    进入官网，点击"注册"按钮，填写个人信息完成注册。若已有账户，点击"登录"并输入凭证。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 2 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 2"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">浏览产品</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    在首页浏览不同产品，点击感兴趣的产品卡片，进入产品页面。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 3 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 3"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">个性化定制</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    在产品页面，根据需求进行个性化定制，选择适合您的配置选项。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer step-primary"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 4 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 4"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">体验产品</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    确定个性化配置后，点击"体验"或"开始"按钮，立即畅享我们的产品和服务。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 5 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 5"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">获取支持与帮助</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    如有任何疑问或需要帮助，可点击页面右下角的"帮助"按钮，联系我们的客户支持团队。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li
                class="step cursor-pointer"
                x-bind:class="{ 'step-primary': tab === 6 }"
                x-on:click="tab = 6"
              >
                <div class="text-start py-4">
                  <div class="text-lg">参与社区互动</div>
                  <div class="text-base-content/80 mt-2">
                    探索网站中的社区板块，参与讨论、分享体验，与其他用户交流互动。
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <img
            loading="lazy"
            class="lg:w-3/5 md:w-1/2 object-cover object-center rounded-lg"
            src="/img/signup.jpg"
            alt="step"
            x-show="tab === 1"
            style="display: none;"
          /><img
            loading="lazy"
            class="lg:w-3/5 md:w-1/2 object-cover object-center rounded-lg"
            src="/img/browse.jpg"
            alt="step"
            x-show="tab === 2"
            style="display: none;"
          /><img
            loading="lazy"
            class="lg:w-3/5 md:w-1/2 object-cover object-center rounded-lg"
            src="/img/customization.jpg"
            alt="step"
            x-show="tab === 3"
            style="display: none;"
